    OMAPDSS: HDMI5: disable interlace modes
    
    We don't support interlace modes properly on OMAP5+ HDMI, so we need to
    reject interlace timings.
    
    Signed-off-by: Tomi Valkeinen <tomi.valkeinen@ti.com>

